# 🇵🇹 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Portugal Readiness

This folder contains the official readiness brief and strategic expansion plan for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II rollout in Portugal.

📄 [Download Portugal Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Portugal_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 📌 Key Highlights

- Strong alignment with EU AI Act and GDPR
- Centralized public health system (SNS)
- Digital health leadership via SPMS (Shared Services of the Ministry of Health)
- Government openness to public-private AI innovation pilots
- Bilingual rollout: Portuguese (required) + English (permitted for demos and pilots)

---

## 🏛️ Governance & Innovation Partners

- SPMS – Shared Services of the Ministry of Health
- CNPD – Comissão Nacional de Proteção de Dados (Portuguese DPA)
- Ministry of Health – Portugal
- Portuguese National Health Service (SNS)
- Key AI-focused institutions: Champalimaud Foundation, Hospital de Santa Maria, São João University Hospital

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization

| Language      | Status  |
|---------------|---------|
| **Portuguese** | ✅ Official; required for compliance and public health documentation |
| **English**    | ✅ Used in health tech and public-private collaboration settings |

🟢 Bilingual pilot dashboards (Portuguese + English) supported and recommended.

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload the PDF readiness brief
- Begin outreach to SPMS and CNPD for pilot opportunities
- Localize dashboards and GDPR automation tools in Portuguese
